<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SocialHub - Sign Up</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-pY1VZsLw8BE7Dp7u7P7sTnZ2H9g6uQvR1gV7wbYw5Q+G5F2hqWCvEYuW1kly7Vd4Y0QlUoJYCK6LoM9Q1xFQiw==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 16% 20%, rgba(56,189,248,0.18), transparent 22%),
                  radial-gradient(circle at 86% 12%, rgba(168,85,247,0.16), transparent 18%),
                  linear-gradient(180deg, #020617 0%, #071223 60%, #020617 100%);
    }
    .page-shell {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }
    .layout-card {
      width: min(100%, 1140px);
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 2.25rem;
      background: rgba(9, 14, 32, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.12);
      box-shadow: 0 48px 140px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      position: relative;
    }
    .layout-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -12% 0 55%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56,189,248,0.14), transparent 70%);
      filter: blur(60px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .panel {
      position: relative;
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    }
    .panel--left {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.08);
    }
    .panel--right {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.94) 0%, rgba(15,23,42,0.84) 100%);
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 4vw, 4.5rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 36rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.82;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .feature-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .feature-card {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 1.85rem;
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.76);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.08);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #7dd3fc;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .form-shell {
      max-width: 34rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.4rem;
    }
    .brand-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
      color: #bae6fd;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.18);
      max-width: fit-content;
    }
    .form-heading {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.05;
    }
    .form-subtext {
      margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .input-group {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .input-label {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .input-field {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.15rem 1.4rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.18);
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.94);
      color: #f8fafc;
      outline: none;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .input-field::placeholder {
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .input-field:focus {
      border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.85);
      background: rgba(15,23,42,1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
    }
    .submit-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #ffffff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8 0%, #818cf8 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(56,189,248,0.22);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    }
    .submit-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 26px 72px rgba(56,189,248,0.28);
    }
    .meta-note {
      margin: 0;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .meta-note a {
      color: #7dd3fc;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer-copy {
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .panel--left {
        border-right: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.08);
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page-shell {
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }
      .panel {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <div class="layout-card grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr]">
      <section class="panel panel--left">
        <div class="brand-pill"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Premium onboarding</div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="hero-title">Create a refined social profile with beautiful sharing.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">Sign up for SocialHub to join a premium community feed designed for thoughtful posts, polished interactions, and a modern visual experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Elegant posts</h3>
            <p>Every post card is crafted to look premium and easy to scan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Secure signup</h3>
            <p>Strong form styling with clear validation and confidence-building layout.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Community focus</h3>
            <p>Designed for a social feed that feels both modern and trustworthy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel panel--right">
        <div class="form-shell">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-sky-400/15 text-sky-300 text-xl"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i></span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs">Create account</p>
              <h2 class="form-heading">Welcome to SocialHub</h2>
            </div>
          </div>

          <form action="/register" method="post" class="grid gap-5">
            <div class="input-group">
              <label class="input-label" for="name">Full name</label>
              <input id="name" type="text" name="name" placeholder="John Doe" required class="input-field" />
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
              <label class="input-label" for="username">Username</label>
              <input id="username" type="text" name="username" placeholder="johndoe" required class="input-field" />
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
              <label class="input-label" for="email">Email address</label>
              <input id="email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="john@example.com" required class="input-field" />
            </div>
            <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="input-group">
                <label class="input-label" for="age">Age</label>
                <input id="age" type="number" name="age" placeholder="18" required class="input-field" />
              </div>
              <div class="input-group">
                <label class="input-label" for="password">Password</label>
                <input id="password" type="password" name="password" placeholder="••••••••" required class="input-field" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-button"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Create account</button>
          </form>

          <p class="meta-note">Already have an account? <a href="/login">Sign in</a> to continue.</p>
          <p class="footer-copy">© 2026 SocialHub. Designed for a premium social experience.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>